game.name: Missile Outbreak
game.description:
It is time to practice your shooting abilities in an environment like never before! Would you like to give it a try especially when you seek for something entertaining and thrilling? If yes, Missile Outbreak is a perfect solution for you. In this brand new action-packed challenge, you have to defend your world from the sudden missile attack. There is a panic amongst the people of your country and you are their only hope. Destroy all those deadly missiles to make them believe on you once again!
Your fighting spirit has made you a nice option for this space battle. Put your quick reflexes and amazing focus abilities to stop those deadly missiles from coming to your planet! You cannot take your steps back since you are the only one who knows how to deal with this situation. These missiles will keep coming from the sky in different waves. You as a savour have to use your weapon to stop them in the sky and make sure that they do not touch your planet. 
Try to survive for as long as possible to create your own score in this HTML5 shooting game! The longer you survive the higher score you will be able to make. Track your score by having a look at the top left corner of the screen! Do not bother if you fail in scoring good initially as you have unlimited chances to beat your previous score. Good luck to survive for as long as possible while clearing all these life-threatening missiles from the sky to create your own high score!
